Package com.github.wuic.nut.core

Package where nuts and their builers implementations are defined for core module.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ByteArrayNut Represents an in-memory nut which can be created on the fly in any context.
ClasspathNutDaoBuilder Builder for nut access in classpath.
CompositeNut A composite Nut is able to chain all the stream provided by each element of the composition.
DiskNutDao A NutDao implementation for disk accesses.
DiskNutDaoBuilder Builder for nut access on disk.
FilePathNut Represents a nut on the path system provided or to be managed by the WUIC framework.
HttpNut A Nut implementation for HTTP accesses.
HttpNutDao A NutDao implementation for HTTP accesses.
HttpNutDaoBuilder Builder for nut access over HTTP.
NotReachableNut This class represents a nut that is not reachable.
PathNutDao A NutDao implementation for accesses based on the path API provided by WUIC.
 

Package com.github.wuic.nut.core Description

Package where nuts and their builers implementations are defined for core module.

HTTP, DISK and CLASSPATH strategies are supported here.
